OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely dry day with a mix of
OL,6,Fcloud and sunny spells, though the odd
OL,7,Flight shower is still possible.
OL,8,FBreezy, especially over the hills with
OL,9,Ftemperatures around average.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry this evening with clear
OL,12,Fspells initially. Cloud building
OL,13,Fovernight with winds strengthening,
OL,14,Fbut remaining dry across the region.
OL,15,FMild.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FA few bright breaks to
OL,18,Fstart, otherwise becoming cloudy and
OL,19,Fwindy with outbreaks of rain, locally
OL,20,Fheavy at times. Milder by day, but
OL,21,Fturning colder overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
