OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FColder
OL,6,Fwith some blustery showers on Friday,
OL,7,Fpossibly wintry. A frosty start to
OL,8,FSaturday, then largely dry and sunny
OL,9,Fspells. Becoming cloudier through
OL,10,FSunday with outbreaks of rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
